snippet.title: The Settlings Official Gameplay 2023 Trailer
snippet.description:
Relaxing settlement builder & resource management game in nostalgic pixelart optic. Gather, deliver, build & fight - All this in your own pace with atmospheric music and many unique mechanics!
#indiegame #citybuilder #pixelart #solodev
